---
title: Garlic-Herb Salmon & Roasted Potatoes with Lemony Veggies & Parsley Yoghurt
description: It’s the queen-bee of fish tonight - blushing pink salmon. This one has been generously spiced with our garlic and herb seasoning before being seared to tender perfection. To accompany, we have roasty potatoes, lemony veg and a fresh and tangy sauce. No one could resist this much tastiness.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
